        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>21st Century Tools for Pain and Addiction Treatment Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Food and Drug Administration (FDA)to revise how it will address the challenges and barriers of developing non-addictive medical products to treat pain or addiction. </p>]]></text>
